# General Flutter/Dart Guidelines

## Code Style

- Prefer const constructors where possible
- Use trailing commas for better formatting
- Follow existing code patterns in the file

## Error Handling

- Check linter errors after making changes
- Fix any introduced errors before completing

## Provider Pattern

- Use Provider.of(context) or CustomProvider.of(context) patterns
- Pass listen: false when not rebuilding on changes
